    dc:description "FIGURES 47 – 52. Stethantyx punarenasa sp. nov., Ƥ: 47 — mesosoma, left; 48 — mesoscutum and scutellum, dorsal; 49 — propodeum, dorsal. Stethantyx sanjosea sp. nov., Ƥ: 50 — mesosoma, dorsal. Stethantyx cartagoa sp. nov., Ƥ: 51 — mesosoma, left; 52 — propodeum, dorsal. Scale bars = 0.1 mm." ;
